                  <rs id="t18770108-170-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18770108-170-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18770108-170-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>, Stealing a ring, the property of <persName id="t18770108-name-122" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18770108-name-122" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18770108-name-122" type="surname" value="WELLS"></interp>
